title: 820-00875 on but no image
message:
keyboard have led blink  and
d8410   pin no1      6v  to   10
d8410 pin  no 2      53v

title: 820-00875 on but no image
message:
History fault, liquid spill, where?

Do you mean 53V at PPVOUT_S0_LCDBKLT?
In this case, bad LED on display, or cable.
Can also be bad LCD connector.
Try new assembly.
